Interstitial State
Check interstitialState at game start. If the state is opened, immediately mute audio and pause gameplay (or rely on the universal platform AUDIO_STATE_CHANGED / PAUSE_STATE_CHANGED handlers — see the note below).

Track state changes to drive ad-specific logic. For muting and pausing, prefer the universal platform events described below instead of reacting to each ad state separately.


